  <h2>Risks to Valuation</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Macroeconomic Cyclicality:</strong> Honeywell is exposed to broader economic cycles. An industrial downturn could stall growth below our 8% base case.</li>
    <li><strong>Aerospace Exposure:</strong> A significant portion of revenue relies on aviation. Disruptions in travel or aircraft manufacturing impact results.</li>
    <li><strong>M&A Integration:</strong> Honeywell frequently engages in acquisitions. Poor integration or overpaying could erode shareholder value.</li>
  </ul>

